{
  "stem": "25773.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a heavenly picture-- young men sitting around a fire, drinking and eating, waiting for the meat to-- to grill, and singing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The sky was blue.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was still light.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The sky was blue.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And these voices were heavenly voices.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They sang so beautifully that, you know, it was-- it was unbelievable what was happening-- the war, the Germans, the killings, the things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were invited to it, but we were afraid-- so Stefan and Masia, and I, and Janina, we were afraid.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we had to join a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were given a little meat and a little vodka, which we were obliged to drink.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then that's how lasted every day, something like that, because they were marching and marching for Berlin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, chasing the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when one batch-- the first batch-- came, it was all right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But after a day-- maybe it was a day or two or three-- was a little bit Poles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then the other-- another-- number of soldiers came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They devastate that village with the food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we watched-- and some of them, when they were in a nice, jolly mood, they just rolled up their hand, and there were watches-- one, one, one, one.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "From here to there, were watches-- here to there-- women's watches, men's watches, whatever they could.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Took from people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they left, we were missing all the watches in the-- in the-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kunat was missing his-- his clocks and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they behaved nicely towards us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was then.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was 1945.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember in 1945, I didn't yet know that it's the end of the-- we were liberated, but it was not the end of the war, because the Germans were going on Berlin.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
